{"tid":2300938,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"百度地圖涉竊14億用戶資料　遭Google Play強制下架","createTime":"2020-11-26T02:33:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T15:20:29.000Z","uid":185631,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"60c345844b309b4ca5e4edd498f6096599eaedd3","tid":2300938,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:33:46.000Z","msg":"中國科技巨頭百度近日被資訊安全公司踢爆，其開發的兩個應用程式「百度搜尋」和「百度地圖」，存在洩漏個人資訊的嚴重安全風險。即更換了手機，只要SIM卡沒有換掉，系統依然可持續追蹤用家的一舉一動。Google分析情況後，認為百度違反了某些政策，已將百度地圖從Google Play商店下架。<br />\n<br />\n美國資訊安全公司Palo Alto Networks日前發布報告，指在Google Play發現多款危險的應用程式，包含「百度搜尋」及「百度地圖」，兩款應用程式在全球的下載總數更達14億次。<br />\n<br />\nPalo Alto Networks指，兩款程式的軟件開發套件（Software Development Kit，SDK）內「PUSH」功能，除了可以獲取用戶的手機型號、屏幕解析度、Android ID等基本資訊外，還會積極收集IMEI、IMSI和MAC地址傳回公司中國總部。<br />\n<br />\n據資料顯示，IMEI主要用來持續追蹤特定手機，而IMSI則是與SIM卡有關。Palo Alto Networks指出，就算用戶更換手機，只要SIM卡沒有換掉，3個資訊加起來，系統理論上仍可得知用戶正在用哪部手機，再使用百度地圖定位系統，就清楚知道人在何方。<br />\n<br />\n根據Android開發指南，Google並不建議開發者收集IMSI、MAC地址等資訊。因此Google於10月28日移除全球市場上的百度搜尋及百度地圖。不過目前百度搜尋已於11月19日重新上架，而百度地圖則仍處於下架狀態。<br />\n<br />\n據Forbes報道指，百度就事件作出回應，稱正努力按照Google指示修正百度地圖，並期望在12月初重返Google Play。惟該企依然未解釋程式為何被下架。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2812853/%E3%80%90%E8%BF%BD%E8%B9%A4%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E3%80%91%E7%99%BE%E5%BA%A6%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96%E6%B6%89%E7%AB%8A14%E5%84%84%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E3%80%80%E9%81%ADGoogle%20Play%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6?mtc=20040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2812853%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E8%25B9%25A4%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2588%25B6%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%2599%25BE%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259C%2596%25E6%25B6%2589%25E7%25AB%258A14%25E5%2584%2584%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2588%25B6%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599%25E3%2580%2580%25E9%2581%25ADGoogle%2520Play%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%259E%25B6%3Fmtc%3D20040&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwvroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=4e1141ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2812853/%E3%80%90%E8%BF%BD%E8%B9%A4%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E3%80%91%E7%99%BE%E5%BA%A6%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96%E6%B6%89%E7%AB%8A14%E5%84%84%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E3%80%80%E9%81%ADGoogle%20Play%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6?mtc=20040</a>"},{"pid":"dd5151188d5b31114dbbdba66b35d8c4e1a59b2c","tid":2300938,"uid":280593,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:35:17.000Z","msg":"14億大陸人？<br />\n正常外國人邊會用"},{"pid":"1a5a9992c4c0f95c7ea53395dd8c6b1f38085bff","tid":2300938,"uid":177089,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"dd5151188d5b31114dbbdba66b35d8c4e1a59b2c","tid":2300938,"uid":280593,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:35:17.000Z","msg":"14億大陸人？<br />\n正常外國人邊會用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:40:02.000Z","msg":"如果唔係點會啱啱好14億<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e541ea0bbdc13f675a2934c91bd48e480b9d0d6","tid":2300938,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:57:09.000Z","msg":"仲有高德地圖柅？"},{"pid":"cb3fd2c10b8639f08ecb930ef77639e6d7b2394e","tid":2300938,"uid":285166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T04:00:36.000Z","msg":"Cls  監控科技領先世界"},{"pid":"682af2a4e32d07556fd0a8829c81935d79157f48","tid":2300938,"uid":62554,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dd5151188d5b31114dbbdba66b35d8c4e1a59b2c","tid":2300938,"uid":280593,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:35:17.000Z","msg":"14億大陸人？<br />\n正常外國人邊會用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T04:06:57.000Z","msg":"去中國咪要用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無選擇"},{"pid":"7d61f1be9ae40bce9bc7313c4e3977099b201a28","tid":2300938,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T